| Q-6 | 🟢 BAJA | [ChatWindow.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/src/components/common/messaging/ChatWindow.tsx) accede a metadata sin tipo | [ChatWindow.tsx:135](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/src/components/common/messaging/ChatWindow.tsx#L135) | [(m as any).metadata?.replyTo](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/src/services/payroll.service.test.ts#282-285) — debería tipar el mensaje con un campo metadata |

